# Normalize all text files to LF on checkout + commit (cross-platform).
# Overrides local core.autocrlf so Windows checkouts no longer introduce CRLF,
# which previously made `bun run lint` (prettier/prettier endOfLine:lf) fail
# locally even though the repo HEAD is LF and CI is green.
# Binary files are auto-detected (NUL-byte heuristic) and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
